                        <interp inst="t18571123-76-offence-2" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>The prisoner was again indicted for stealing a pair of gloves of <persName id="t18571123-name-556" type="victimName">
                           <interp inst="t18571123-name-556" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                           <interp inst="t18571123-name-556" type="surname" value="WHITTER"></interp>
