                           <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18571123-76-offence-2 t18571123-name-556"></join>Solomon Whitter</persName>, his master,</rs> on which <rs id="t18571123-76-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18571123-76-verdict-2" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18571123-76-verdict-2" type="verdictSubcategory" value="noEvidence"></interp>no evidence was offered.</rs>
                  </hi>)</p>
